com.example.habitup.Model

Class HabitEventCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.habitup.Model.HabitEventCommand

  • public class HabitEventCommand
extends java.lang.Object
    HabitEventCommand is how we handle offline behaviors around HabitEvents: each action is modeled as a Command, which is stored in a queue, and executed when connectivity is available. Created by Ty on 2017-11-26.
